OL,5, Courts waved through applications by   
OL,6, energy firms to forcibly install       
OL,7, prepayment meters in people's homes,   
OL,8, according to internal advice leaked to 
OL,9, the BBC.                               
OL,11,FPrevious guidelines required careful   
OL,12,Fscrutiny of warrant applications, but  
OL,13,Fnew advice to courts deems those rules 
OL,14,F"disproportionate".                    
OL,16,FEnergy firms can apply for warrants    
OL,17,Fwhen bills go unpaid for a long period.
OL,19,FBut suppliers were told to stop        
OL,20,Fforce-fitting meters earlier this week.
